---
title: "Slade Networks — Finger Lakes Networking"
description: "UniFi network installation and support for homes and small businesses in the Finger Lakes and surrounding areas in upstate NY."
navActive: home
---
{% extends "base.njk" %}

{% block content %}
  <main>

    <section class="hero">
      <div class="wrap">
        <h1>Deploying UniFi Full-Stack Networking in the Finger Lakes</h1>
        <p class="subtext">
          Modern IT infrastructure installation, configuration, and administration for homes and businesses.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="wrap">
        <h2 class="sectionTitle">Wi-Fi, Cameras, VoIP, and More</h2>
        <p class="sectionIntro">
          Real installations across the Finger Lakes — clean work, proper mounting, and systems built to last.
        </p>

        <div class="scrollWrapper" aria-label="Install photos carousel">
          <div class="productScroll">
            <div class="tile"><div class="media"><img src="/assets/IMG_0465.jpeg" alt="Wi-Fi access point installation"></div></div>
            <div class="tile"><div class="media"><img src="/assets/camera-install.jpeg" alt="Camera installation"></div></div>
            <div class="tile"><div class="media"><img src="/assets/IMG_0464.jpeg" alt="VoIP phone installation"></div></div>
            <div class="tile"><div class="media"><img src="/assets/IMG_0431.jpeg" alt="Network rack installation"></div></div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="wrap">
        <h2 class="sectionTitle">Why UniFi</h2>
        <p class="sectionIntro sectionIntroFull">
          UniFi brings networking, Wi-Fi, cameras, and phones into a single pane of glass. That means fewer moving parts, clearer visibility, and a setup that stays reliable and fast over time.
        </p>

        <div class="gridTwo">
          <div class="infoCard">
            <h3>Single pane of glass</h3>
            <p>Manage gateways, switching, Wi-Fi, cameras, and VoIP from one dashboard instead of juggling multiple apps.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="infoCard">
            <h3>Reliability built in</h3>
            <p>Standardized configurations and predictable updates reduce surprises and keep systems stable day-to-day.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="infoCard">
            <h3>Performance you can feel</h3>
            <p>Proper placement, clean RF design, and tuned configurations deliver consistent coverage and throughput.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="infoCard">
            <h3>Supportable over time</h3>
            <p>Optional remote administration helps troubleshoot faster and keep everything running smoothly.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="wrap">
        <h2 class="sectionTitle">Service Area</h2>
        <p class="sectionIntro">Local installs across the Finger Lakes and nearby towns.</p>

        <div class="serviceAreaWrap">
          <div class="serviceAreaSquare serviceAreaCard">
            <h3>Finger Lakes coverage</h3>
            <p>
              Serving Penn Yan, Keuka Park, Hammondsport, Watkins Glen,
              Geneva, Canandaigua, Naples, Victor, Auburn, and Ithaca (case-by-case).
            </p>
            <p>
              If you're slightly outside this area, reach out — travel is often
              possible depending on project size.
            </p>
            <p>
              Typical projects include whole-home Wi-Fi coverage, small business
              network infrastructure, camera systems, and VoIP deployments.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="serviceAreaSquare serviceAreaMap">
            <img src="/assets/service-area-map.png" alt="Slade Networks service area map in the Finger Lakes">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="ctaSection">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="ctaInner">
          <div>
            <h2>Ready to improve your network?</h2>
            <p>Tell us what you're trying to fix or build. We'll respond with next steps and a clear plan.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="ctaButtons">
            <a class="btn primary" href="/contact/">Request a free consultation</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
{% endblock %}
